rows.label: qst300407_msg0001
rows.name:
What are a gaggle of civilians
doing aboard this vessel?

rows.label: qst300407_msg0002
rows.name:
A consignment from a Gulan
mercenary?

rows.label: qst300407_msg0003
rows.name:
Yes, I recall Captain Saffran receiving
a package of that nature. An important
delivery to the homeland, he called it.

rows.label: qst300407_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, I'm afraid he didn't specify
as to the exact contents...

rows.label: qst300407_msg0005
rows.name:
But even if I knew, what good
would it do you when you will not
be leaving this room alive?
